lead_paragraph: U.S. Olympic athletes expressed little sympathy for tennis star Maria Sharapova's revelation that she failed a drug test, saying they wanted sporting officials to raise the pressure for clean play.

headline.main: U.S. Olympians Unsympathetic to Sharapova; Fear Rio Won't Be Clean
